	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Duas decades sermonum tuorum mittente communi amico et domino <persName ref="p8049" cert="high">Ioachimo Vadiano</persName> hodie accepi; Christus noster vindex sit tua retributio, qui inexhausta sua bonitate nunquam etiam in mediis trubinibus et procellis nos deserit, quin a patre luminum semper prophetas extimulet, qui aliquid lucubrentur, unde consolationem sumamus.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego, quia tui sermones ad hęc tempora plurimum factura ex literis <persName ref="p8049" cert="high">Vadiani</persName> intelligo, in eisdem eo intentius versabor.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quo se vestri symmiste omnes atque ubi <persName ref="p8417" cert="high">Musculus</persName> agat et profugi fratres <placeName ref="l491" cert="high">Argentoratenses</placeName>, lubens scirem.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego hic inter Scithas prorsus idolatras dego periculis pluribus expositus.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Numa quidam consului <persName type="citizen_name">Egeriam</persName>, quę respondit brevi gentem confluxuram, quę bellica manu conatura sit omnes cis et ultra <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2459" cert="high">Rhenum</placeName> proximas civitates occupare et postea pactionem non recusaturam.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hic fama est <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8112">Gallum</persName> et <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18538" cert="high">Cesarem</persName> concordiam iniisse, inter <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglum</placeName> quoque et <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18538" cert="high">Cesarem</persName> bene convenire.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Civitates <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l749">Saxonię</placeName>, etiam illę, quę dicionibus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18250">ducis Mauricii</persName> subiacent, deinde quoque <persName type="auto_name" ref="p3671">rex Danię</persName>, dux Augustus, frater Mauricii, duces <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l743" cert="high">Pomeranię</placeName> ac marchio <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1048" cert="high">Brandenburgensis</placeName> <persName type="auto_name">Ioannes</persName> novam ecclesię ordinationem Interim nondum receperunt, mori se potius affirmantes quam in id consensuros.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De quo parum dubito.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nihilo minus hic annus illis marcialia ingentia non minatur.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quidam putant proditorem illum in propria viscera amplius seviturum, sed subtili modo.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">uxor legitima landgraphii ab <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l213">Hessia</placeName> fertur ad dominum migrasse, ipsum vero datis duobus filiis vadibus ex captivitate brevi liberandum.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Filii capti ducis <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p19065">Ioannis Friderichi</persName> recusant Interim constanter; propterea eos patria calamitas manet.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale, mi anime.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Salveant universi fratres, <persName ref="p8011" cert="high">Gualtherus</persName> etc.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Raptim ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l245" cert="high">Kauffburna</placeName> 18. Aprilis 1549.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName ref="p8354" cert="high">G[eorgius] L[aetus</persName>].</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse:]</note>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro D. <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Henricho Bullingero</persName>, antistiti apud <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tigurinos</placeName> vigilantissimo, domino et amico observandissimo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
